'''乳木果油'''是由由非洲特有植物[[乳油木|乳油木]](Vitellaria paradoxa) 之堅果所榨取的[[植物油|植物性油脂]]<ref name="Ullmann">{{cite encyclopedia|author=Alfred Thomas|title=Fats and Fatty Oils|encyclopedia=Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry|publisher=Wiley-VCH|place=Weinheim|year=2002|doi=10.1002/14356007.a10_173}}</ref>。外觀呈象牙色澤，化學成分主要由硬[[硬脂酸|硬脂酸]]和[[油酸|油酸]]衍生的[[甘油三酯|三酸甘油酯]]所構成。它被廣泛使用於[[化妝品|化妝品]]當中，作為[[潤膚膏|潤膚膏]]、藥膏或洗劑。乳木果油是可食用的，在[[非洲|非洲]]會把它用於製作食品<ref name="Lost crops of Africa">{{cite book|url=http://books.nap.edu/openbook.php?record_id=11763&page=303|title=Lost Crops of Africa: Volume II: Vegetables (2006)|isbn=978-0-309-10333-6|author=National Research Council|access-date=2017-03-03|archive-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113063245/http://books.nap.edu/openbook.php?record_id=11763&page=303|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[巧克力|巧克力]]工業偶爾會使用乳木果油跟其他油混合作為[[可可脂|可可脂]]的代替品，儘管在味道上明顯不同<ref name="sheatreeproducts">{{cite web|url=http://www.fao.org/docrep/008/y5918e/y5918e11.htm|title=Reinforcing sound management through trade: shea tree products in Africa|author=E. T. Masters, J. A. Yidana and P. N. Lovett|year=2004|accessdate=2017-03-03|archive-date=2019-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190216172744/http://www.fao.org/docrep/008/y5918e/y5918e11.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.inra.fr/sae2/publications/cahiers/pdf/fold.pdf|title=A matter of good taste? Quality and the construction of standards for chocolate in the European Union. ''Cahiers d’Economie et Sociologie Rurales'', 55/56: 92–110|author=Fold, N. 2000.|accessdate=2017-03-03|archive-date=2012-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120410045348/http://www.inra.fr/sae2/publications/cahiers/pdf/fold.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[英語|英語]]字詞「乳木果 (shea)」是源自[[馬里|馬里]][[班巴拉语|班巴拉語]]的一種樹木名稱<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/shea?s=t|title=Reference.com Dictionary Entry|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304061502/http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/shea?s=t|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它有很多本地已知的名稱，例如：[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]][[沃洛夫語|沃洛夫語]]的''karité'' <ref name="goreja">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6iQjwr9v84gC&printsec=frontcover&dq=shea+butter&hl=en&sa=X&ei=jkX5ULH7McijigKBp4HoBw&ved=0CEAQ6AEwAQ|title=Shea Butter: The Nourishing Properties of Africa's Best-Kept Natural Beauty Secret|last=Goreja|first=W. G.|publisher=TNC International|accessdate=|year=2004|origyear=|isbn=9780974296258|edition=|volume=|page=5|pages=|chapter=Chapter 2|oclc=|editorn-last=|editorn-first=|place=|archive-date=2020-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200912165510/https://books.google.com/books?id=6iQjwr9v84gC&printsec=frontcover&dq=shea+butter&hl=en&sa=X&ei=jkX5ULH7McijigKBp4HoBw&ved=0CEAQ6AEwAQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[西非|西非]]的一些地方會稱作ori，以及許多其他名稱<ref>{{cite web|url=http://products.skinglowbykimmarie.com/ori_shea_butter.htm|title=Shea Butter|accessdate=2013-03-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130301160548/http://products.skinglowbykimmarie.com/ori_shea_butter.htm|archivedate=2013-03-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://skinglowbykimmarie.com/blog/?page_id=2|title=Ori Shea Butter|accessdate=2013-03-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130119021429/http://skinglowbykimmarie.com/blog/?page_id=2|archivedate=2013-01-19}}</ref>。
